data.description: Price Reduction!! Come take a look at this highly sought out Western Meadows Subdivision home in far North Valley. Homes in this area have shared Bridal Trail in back of lot to access Bosque trails for horse back riding, hiking, and biking. In a private and quiet neighborhood with circular drive way. House has 5 bedrooms 3 bathrooms with a large living room on a large corner lot .62 acres with back yard access and 3 private wells on property and a two year roof. Make this your home today!
